title: Momos
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Organic, Juice bar, Take-out, Fusion, Nepalese
description: Cozy organic vegan-vegetarian eatery specializing in dumplings inspired by the Nepalese momo, a typical Himalayan street food. Dumplings may be ordered steamed, pan-fried, or served in broth as momo soup. Everything is made in-house with organic ingredients. Also serving fresh juices. Eco-friendly recycable packaging is used for takeaway orders. Since Apr 2013.
